Peter-Kay-and-Jimmy-Savile-696x455.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Peter-Kay-and-Jimmy-Savile-1392x911.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Peter-Kay-and-Jimmy-Savile-1068x699.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2036px) 100vw, 2036px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/peter-kay">彼得·凯 (Peter Kay)</a>公开谈论了与吉米·萨维尔 (Jimmy Saville) 的合作，并将这位名誉扫地的主持人描述为“肮脏的老变态”。</p><p>在他的新书<em>《小屏幕上的大冒险》</em>发行之前，凯在接受<a href="https://www.mirror.co.uk/3am/celebrity-news/peter-kay-creepy-jimmy-savile-31056041?_ga=2.70535061.420970499.1696011275-1846600422.1696011273" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《镜报》</em></a>采访时回忆了他职业生涯的一些高潮和低谷，包括与萨维尔的合作。</p><p>这位喜剧演员表示，他正在为<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/bbc">BBC</a>电视剧<em>《周日秀》</em>制作<em>彼得·凯的《娱乐世界》</em>的最后一集，并希望通过让萨维尔参与来“把船推出去”。 Jim&#39;ll Fix It 的主持人同意了，理由是他将收到 500 英镑现金和一盒价值 1000 英镑的雪茄，凯也同意了。</p><p> However, Kay said he found Savile to be “very eccentric”, claiming he “talked utter nonsense, spouting weird quotes, crap jokes, limericks”.</p><p> Kay continued: “The only hint I got of Jimmy being immoral in any way was when he met our executive producer, Bridget Boseley.</p><p> “I remember she offered him her hand, which Jimmy took, then he flipped it round to kiss the back of it, but before his lips touched her skin I saw a quick flick of his tongue licking the back of her hand.呃！那是怎么回事？</p><p> “Bridget and I chatted about it later. She said, &#39;He licked the back of my hand,&#39;” to which Kay replied:”I know, I saw him, the dirty old perv.” </p><figure id="attachment_3503647" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3503647" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3503647" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Peter-Kay-main.jpg" alt="彼得·凯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Peter-Kay-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Peter-Kay-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Peter-Kay-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Peter-Kay-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Peter-Kay-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Peter-Kay-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3503647" class="wp-caption-text"> Peter Kay. CREDIT: Stuart C. Wilson/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> Kay also detailed the time he was asked to help cover up images of Savile&#39;s face with Children in Need stickers during an event at the BBC Media City HQ in Salford — the day after the ITV documentary exposing the presenter aired.</p><p> Kay wrote in his book: “Everybody had gone apart from Peter Salmon (BBC Exec), Guy Garvey, Mr Tumble and me.主走廊的墙上有一幅巨大的黑白壁画，上面有多年来 BBC 的标志。 Michael Parkinson, <em>Only Fools and Horses</em> , <em>Dad&#39;s Army</em> , that sort of thing. Just like wallpaper, the images repeated along the length of the wall.</p><p> “I&#39;ll never forget Peter Salmon, he said, &#39;Here, could you do me a favour?&#39; and he handed each of us a pile of big bright-yellow Children in Need Pudsey Bear stickers. &#39;Could you find Savile and cover him up?&#39;</p><p> “So there we were, up step ladders trying to find every image of Jimmy Savile so we could cover him up (ironically just what the BBC had reportedly been doing for years).就像一个堕落的人沃利在哪里？ Or Where&#39;s Jimmy?”</p><p> Elsewhere, Kay recently expressed his desire to <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/peter-kay-wants-to-revive-phoenix-nights-film-3503639">revive his hit sitcom <em>Phoenix Nights</em> for a feature film</a> .</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/peter-kay-recalls-dirty-old-perv-jimmy-savile-licking-female-bbc-executives-hand-3506781">Peter Kay recalls “dirty old perv” Jimmy Savile licking female BBC executive&#39;s hand</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
